WEBVTT

00:13:28.160 --> 00:13:31.321
we need journalists who are prepared,

00:13:31.345 --> 00:13:32.916
at any given moment,

00:13:32.940 --> 00:13:34.734
to set neutrality aside.

00:13:35.357 --> 00:13:38.195
Personally, I feel like
I've been preparing for this moment

00:13:38.219 --> 00:13:39.373
my whole life.

00:13:39.397 --> 00:13:41.683
When they censored me when I was 24,

00:13:41.707 --> 00:13:48.377
I learned that neutrality, fear
and silence often make you an accomplice

00:13:48.401 --> 00:13:50.258
in crime, abuse

00:13:50.847 --> 00:13:52.394
and injustice.

00:13:52.418 --> 00:13:54.443
And being an accomplice to power

00:13:54.467 --> 00:13:57.007
is never good journalism.

00:13:57.574 --> 00:14:00.244
Now, at 59 years old,